Title: Renormalization of Functional Schroedinger Equation by Background Field
  Method
Author: K.Zarembo
Comments: 9pp., Latex
Journal-ref: Mod.Phys.Lett. A13 (1998) 1709-1718
\\
  Renormalization group transformations for Schr\"odinger equation are
performed in $\phi^4$ and in Yang-Mills theories. The dependence of the ground
state wave functional on rapidly oscillating fields is found. For Yang-Mills
theory, this dependence restricts a possible form of variational ansatz
compatible with asymptotic freedom.
